1: Split the system into 3 actors.
        - System
        - Relay    
        - Client
        
2: (Some) routers can use FFMPEG. (Let's just assume all we have possess the ability to do so)
   https://hackaday.io/project/167224-router-becomes-video-recorder-for-ip-cameras

3: FFMPEG pode ser usado para retransmitir ffmpeg streams (tcp/udp)
   https://lists.ffmpeg.org/pipermail/ffmpeg-user/2012-August/009203.html
